title: Friday Night Funkin' - Ugh but everytime it's Tankman turn a Different Skin Mod and Cover is used
author: PrizMatex
description:
Today's video is another combination of Friday Night Funkin Ugh songs which is High Effort Ugh 2.0, Stop Posting About Among Us but its Ugh, Ruv Singing Ugh, Whitty Sings Ugh (better version), Roses but Ugh, Sky Sings Ugh/Uhrgg, Selever Sings Ugh, and Ugh but the Mom Sings it while using different skin mods of course. Honestly, I'm impressed at how much of meme this song has become that almost everyone in the Friday Night Funkin' community wants every different character to sing Ugh. Once again I still want people to know that I did use a bot to keep things well sync because I don't intend on hiding that fact since I wanted to make this video as a fun viewing experience while delivering people exposure of new skin mods out there. Overall, love the unique input for each character and I'm even more shocked at how well it fits with the actual song.
